title: Philosophy Supernatural Airbrushed Canvas Powder, SPF 15, Bronze
description: Super Natural CoverageWhat conceals, camouflages and provides SPF protection all in one easy step? The Supernatural Airbrushed Canvas SPF 15 from Philosophy. This multi-tasking powder formula provides sheer, natural coverage and leaves the skin with a smooth, airbrushed appearance.A sheer, multi-tasking high-pigment powderServes as a foundation, concealer, powder and SPF in oneProvides sheer, natural coverage and a smooth, airbrushed appearanceThe lightweight formula and incredibly fast and easy-to-use sponge applicator makes this gentle powder safe to use on all skin types - from the most sensitive, to the most prone to breakouts.Especially Suited For:All skin typesFree of:Parabens, synthetic fragrances, talc, water, oilFor Best Effect:Turn the container over, and lightly tap to fill sponge applicator with powder.
